name: Oracle
queryCode:
SELECT
t1.ACCESSID,
t1.ACCESSNAME,
t1.ACCESS_KEY,
t1.ACCESS_TOKEN,
t1.AGENT_ID,
t1.CALLBACK_PARAM,
t1.CALLBACK_PARAM2,
t1.CALLBACK_TOKEN,
t1.DEFAULTFLAG,
t1.DISABLED,
t1.EXPIRES_TIME,
t1.ISMOBACCAPP,
t1.NOTIFY_URL,
t1.OPEN_TYPE,
t1.ORGID,
t1.REDIRECT_URI,
t1.REGION_ID,
t1.SECRET_KEY
FROM (
         SELECT
             t1.ACCESSID,
             t1.ACCESSNAME,
             t1.ACCESS_KEY,
             t1.ACCESS_TOKEN,
             t1.AGENT_ID,
             t1.CALLBACK_PARAM,
             t1.CALLBACK_PARAM2,
             t1.CALLBACK_TOKEN,
             t1.DEFAULTFLAG,
             t1.DISABLED,
             t1.EXPIRES_TIME,
             t1.ISMOBACCAPP,
             t1.NOTIFY_URL,
             t1.OPEN_TYPE,
             t1.ORGID,
             t1.REDIRECT_URI,
             t1.REGION_ID,
             t1.SECRET_KEY
         FROM IBZOPENACCESS t1
         union
         SELECT
             t1.ID as ACCESSID,
             t1.NAME as ACCESSNAME,
             t1.ACCESS_KEY,
             t1.ACCESS_TOKEN,
             t1.AGENT_ID,
             t1.AGENT_ID as CALLBACK_PARAM,
             t1.REGION_ID as CALLBACK_PARAM2,
             t1.ACCESS_TOKEN as CALLBACK_TOKEN,
             0 as DEFAULTFLAG,
             t1.DISABLED,
             t1.EXPIRES_TIME,
             null as ISMOBACCAPP,
             t1.REDIRECT_URI as NOTIFY_URL,
             t1.OPEN_TYPE,
             null as ORGID,
             t1.REDIRECT_URI,
             t1.REGION_ID,
             t1.SECRET_KEY
         FROM OPEN_ACCESS t1
         where ENABLED = 1 and not exists(select 1 from IBZOPENACCESS where ACCESSID = t1.ID)
     ) t1
